    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 premium SUV is a fantastic example of a well-maintained vehicle that balances luxury with practical reliability. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical marks of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is plush and intact, with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the heated seats and intuitive infotainment system, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history showing regular synthetic oil changes. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With recent brake service and tires that still have plenty of life, this SUV is ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
